                              String level)
        Constructor for the FinishCreationListener-class.
        Parameters:
        txtname - user inputs name of the level
        txtlives - user inputs the amount of lives for the level
        txttime - user inputs the timeframe in which the level is supposed to be completed
        pPerSec - user inputs the amount of points player gets for compliting the level in time
        xtrapoints - Radiobutton used to enable extra points for every second faster than the given timeframe when compliting the level
        deadline - Radiobutton used to enable the absolute timeframe in which the level must be completed or the level will be failed
        fillbubbles - Radiobutton used to fill all empty spaces in the level with pointbubbles
        finished - Button that directs to the startmenu and saves the created level if all inputs are acceptable
        wh - windowhandler used to change the content on the screen
        level - String format of the objectpositioning for the level
